Hello again-

The story (or, at least, a mashup of it) was picked up by KurzweilAI.net.
Kurzweil wrote The Singularity is Near.

Some of the facts were lost in translation, but at least the direct link to
the HyperNEAT user's page made it. That should help HyperNEAT get even more
attention. 

Here is the article:
http://www.kurzweilai.net/artificial-life-forms-evolve-basic-intelligence

If that didn't work, try this:
http://tinyurl.com/KurzweilAI-HyperNEAT
